{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"746e5845-9004-4a20-98b9-29bb9174810c","content":"There are two reliable programmatic approaches — both read from the **workload manifests and SDK packs** that ship with your exact .NET SDK:\n\n### 1. Inspect the Android SDK props (exact versions)\n\n```bash\n# Find your SDK path\nSDK_PATH=$(dotnet --info | grep 'Base Path' | awk '{print $3}')\n\n# The Android workload pack ships a .props file with pinned versions:\nfind \"$(dirname \"$SDK_PATH\")/../packs\" -name 'Xamarin.Android.Sdk.props' | head -1 | xargs grep -E 'AndroidSdkBuildToolsVersion|AndroidApiLevel|AndroidCommandLineToolsVersion'\n```\n\nThis gives you the **exact** values MAUI expects, e.g.:\n\n```xml\n<AndroidSdkBuildToolsVersion>34.0.0</AndroidSdkBuildToolsVersion>\n<AndroidApiLevel>34</AndroidApiLevel>\n<AndroidCommandLineToolsVersion>11.0</AndroidCommandLineToolsVersion>\n```\n\n### 2. Inspect the workload manifest (pack versions & dependencies)\n\n```bash\nBAND=$(dotnet --version | sed 's/\\.[0-9]*$//') # e.g. 8.0.400\nfind \"$SDK_PATH/sdk-manifests\" -path '*android*' -name 'WorkloadManifest.json' \\\n  | head -1 | xargs cat | python3 -m json.tool\n```\n\nThis JSON lists every pack, its version, and which workloads depend on it.\n\n### For CI, the one-liner you want:\n\n```bash\ndotnet new android -o /tmp/_probe && \\\n  dotnet build /tmp/_probe -t:ResolveAndroidTooling -v:n 2>&1 \\\n  | grep -iE 'build-tools|platform-tools|cmdline-tools|platforms;android'\n```\n\nThis actually **resolves** the tooling against your SDK and prints what it needs.\n\n### Summary\n\n| Source | What it tells you |\n|---|---|\n| `Xamarin.Android.Sdk.props` | `BuildToolsVersion`, `ApiLevel`, `CmdLineToolsVersion` |\n| `WorkloadManifest.json` | Pack names, versions, workload graph |\n| `ResolveAndroidTooling` target | Full `sdkmanager` package list |\n\nThe props file is the most reliable for CI — parse those three values and feed them to `sdkmanager install`.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"50fe3e4a-6166-47b8-afdd-f8842f4ca71f","outputTokens":597},"id":"94cc10bb-ddbb-48e5-8e31-993fa05d02dd","timestamp":"2026-04-05T00:52:27.125Z","parentId":"d2beedd6-bfb9-4733-9d9c-ab923933e57e"}
